title: Google Pixel 4a 5G and 4A stuck on oct 1 2020 update for Google Play System Update
content: My pixel 4a and 4a 5G are stuck on oct 1 2020 update for Google Play Store. It turns green to red automatically. When check for update on both devices, it shows oct 1 2020 is the latest. How to get the latest december 2020 update?
